    "answer_id" : 59264567,
    "question_id" : 10332132,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Based on @tetsuo answer, with java 8 :</p>\n<pre><code>Integer i = ...\n\nswitch (Optional.ofNullable(i).orElse(DEFAULT_VALUE)) {\n    case DEFAULT_VALUE:\n        doNull();\n        break;\n    default:\n        doDefault();\n        break;\n\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
